content:
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:ch-scp-theme]]

[[module css]]
#page-content > p {
	padding: 0 1em;
}
@supports (mix-blend-mode: screen) {
	.poem::before {
		mix-blend-mode: darken;
	}
}

@supports ((-webkit-clip-path: url("")) or (clip-path: url(""))) {
	.glitch::before {
		background: rgba(var(--white-monochrome));
	}
	.glitch::after {
		background: rgba(var(--white-monochrome));
	}
}

@supports (((-webkit-mask-image: url("")) or (mask-image: url(""))) or (-webkit-mask-image: url(""))) {
	.sidd:before {
		mask-image:
			-webkit-gradient(
				linear, left top, left bottom,
					from(rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)),
					color-stop(40%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)));
		mask-image:
			linear-gradient(to bottom,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 0%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 40%);
		-webkit-mask-image:
			-webkit-gradient(
				linear, left top, left bottom,
					from(rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)),
					color-stop(40%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)));
		-webkit-mask-image:
			-webkit-linear-gradient(top,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 0%,
				rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 40%);
		-webkit-border-radius: 2em 2em 0 0;
		        border-radius: 2em 2em 0 0;
	}
	.sidd:after {
		--dark-accent: 200, 245, 255;
	}
}

@supports (mix-blend-mode: screen) {
	.sidd:before {
		mix-blend-mode: screen;
	}
}
[[/module]]
[[=]]
> 这篇故事在设计时考虑到了使用银河联邦版式，见于此处：[/the-moons-stellar-companion 联邦版式]。投票结果两页共享，所以您可选择喜欢的版面进行投票。
[[/=]]
